Description: libraVDB daemon — AI-native vector database with ML embeddings
 libravdbd is the daemon component of libraVDB, an AI-native
 vector database for LLM memory and semantic search. It provides
 embeddings, summarization, and vector storage through an RPC
 interface backed by ONNX Runtime.
 .
